{"tid":230521,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益)一人一個玩鳩電話騙徒既方法","createTime":"2017-05-05T12:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T13:05:44.000Z","uid":56028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d522d8a747421f67b47c069e60d3e15ab9cee31","tid":230521,"uid":56028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"第一次打黎自稱csl員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話有個舊客免一年台費既優惠<br />\n<br />\n果陣無為意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己又係舊客 就透露左少少資料比條友<br />\n<br />\n然後諗諗下 自己都唔會用翻csl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就cut左佢線<br />\n<br />\n之後就黎料啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平均一日三四次咁打黎<br />\nblock左佢電話號碼就變133<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/200102_2059ac928376bd949acb8c4e083f7d1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F200102_2059ac928376bd949acb8c4e083f7d1e.jpg&h=f92b55fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有日我頂唔順去csl問 原來根本無咁既優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩佢又打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問下大家有咩方法玩殘個騙徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c46cf63779d87aa700a07c594d1efea04fb551","tid":230521,"uid":66654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:59:03.000Z","msg":"直接報驚"},{"pid":"87260b886bd6fb97c39da217518ad4a667015932","tid":230521,"uid":28704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"佢再打黎就<br />\n<br />\nAngle 方架"}]}